definition: to change/to become different/to transform/to vary/rebellion
capacity/quantity/amount/to estimate/abbr. for 量詞|量词[liang4 ci2], classifier (in Chinese grammar)/measure word

sentences.english: Any processing you would like to do on session variables.
sentences.chinese: 可以對會話變量做任何你想要的處理。

sentences.english: Let's look at this 8th variance of this, otherwise, simple example.
sentences.chinese: 這是這個例子的第8個變量版本，很簡單。

sentences.english: We would like to get rid of x because it is this dependent variable.
sentences.chinese: 我們希望擺脫x，因爲x是一個因變量。

sentences.english: For example, this is the place to store configuration variables that will be provided in FreeRADIUS. conf.
sentences.chinese: 例如，這個地方用來存放配置文件的變量。

sentences.english: The future detailed prices were forecasted by univariate time series models.
sentences.chinese: 用單變量時間序列模型預測未來細節電價。

sentences.english: There are a few more environment variables that relate to serviceability.
sentences.chinese: 還有幾個與可服務性相關的環境變量。

sentences.english: It realizes self-tuning decoupling control for multivariable systems with arbitary delay time structure.
sentences.chinese: 實現了對具有任意延時結構的多變量系統的解耦控制。

sentences.english: By using this method, we can realize the phase-covariant quantum cloning by four steps.
sentences.chinese: 用這種方法，相位協變量子克隆可以通過四步來實現。

sentences.english: Here, you have two variables of integration.
sentences.chinese: 這邊需要對兩個變量做積分。

sentences.english: This is ten to the 12, right? It's still a huge variance.
sentences.chinese: 這是十的12次方，對嗎？它仍然是個巨大的變量。

sentences.english: Note also how complex the interplay of variables can be.
sentences.chinese: 另請注意變量間相互作用的複雜程度。

sentences.english: Given those variations, tsunami experts warned that predicting wave heights was difficult.
sentences.chinese: 考慮到這些變量，海嘯專家們說浪高會很難預測。

sentences.english: Object Invariants are conditions specified for each instances of a class.
sentences.chinese: 對象不變量則爲每個實例指定條件。

sentences.english: Then click OK to set the environment variable.
sentences.chinese: 然後單擊“確定”，以設置此環境變量。

sentences.english: These should have variables map to the location in the execution environment.
sentences.chinese: 這些應該讓變量映射到執行環境中的位置上。

sentences.english: Therefore, the identity transition is an important variable for America to rise in peac…
sentences.chinese: 因此，認同轉換是美國實現和平崛起的重要變量。
